Requirements:

	Android(> 2.2,froyo)

Installation & Usage guidelines:

	1:Download the alipi.apk file from this link hhttps://play.google.com/store/search?q=alipi&c=apps

	3:Click on the alipi.apk follow the instructions to install the application

	4:Start the application and enter a url which has re-narration(a11y.in/a11y_dw/). 
	
	5:After the web-page loads,press the rennaration(green button) in the action bar(at the top)

	6:After choosing the language and author, The web-page loads with the re-narrated content

	7:If audio is present, a audio button appears next to the rennaratibon button. Click on it to choose and listen to the audio